SECTION 2: P0-1 500 Fix Verification
=================================================================
feedback-summary unauthorized (interviewer):
  Before: HTTP 500
  After:  HTTP 404, body={"success":false,"error":"Job not found or access denied"} ✅

mismatched applicationId:
  Before: HTTP 500
  After:  HTTP 400, body={"success":false,"error":"Application does not belong to the specified job"} ✅

invalid sourceFeedbackId:
  Before: HTTP 500
  After:  HTTP 404, body={"success":false,"error":"Source feedback nonexistent not found or access denied"} ✅

Error status mapping in all API routes:
  "Permission denied" → 403
  "not found" / "access denied" → 404
  "does not belong" / "Invalid" → 400
  otherwise → 500

